{"tid":1334511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［港共染指醫療界］香港中大擬修例容許深圳中大醫學生來港執業","createTime":"2019-07-20T06:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T12:45:45.000Z","uid":149092,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e7124afe33fa8d9f4530d6ac012f9e0424d9cdc6","tid":1334511,"uid":149092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:35:02.000Z","msg":"1. <span style=\"color: red;\">香港中大校方承認計劃修改香港法例</span>第1109章《香港中文大學條例》附表1內的《香港中文大學規程》規程26<span style=\"color: red;\">以容許深圳中大畢業生獲頒香港中大醫科學位</span><br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">根據香港法例第161章《醫生註冊條例》</span>，取得條例附表一指明的醫科學位<span style=\"color: red;\">便可以在港實習(臨時註冊)，然後正式註冊。</span>（附表一當然包括香港中大，故根據現行法例，深圳中大醫學院的醫科畢業生可以來港實習和註冊）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">必須撤回，不接受暫緩及語言偽術<br />\n停止染紅教育界及醫療界</span><br />\n<br />\n詳情: 杏林覺醒 M&eacute;decins Inspir&eacute;s <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/enlightenedhealers/posts/2246558692128655\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fenlightenedhealers%2Fposts%2F2246558692128655&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbqooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=f41f1e62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/enlightenedhealers/posts/2246558692128655</a>"},{"pid":"0716a14727a78f26fcda855603653bd5408ee1cf","tid":1334511,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:36:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96cb2935fa474dccff9a83da1c2d295ac33a1572","tid":1334511,"uid":124198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:42:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ade015934bafb64d7d2f25d62af6cd623a9ae5d","tid":1334511,"uid":234765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:18:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9bef89361cad0fcedf97ffb5198868758d7a76d2","tid":1334511,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:19:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[沙盤推演] 